  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You outfit your arms with a device of your own description, allowing your soundwaves to penetrate defenses. You may use this gadget as a ninja tool component with Otogi hijutsu you cast that makes an attack roll. When you do so, if the jutsu makes a ranged attack roll, it instead becomes a melee attack roll using your unarmed strike. A jutsu cast this cannot have its damage be reduced by more than 5. As a bonus action, when you deal force damage to a creature using an Otogi hijutsu this way, you can spend a charge to force advantage on your attack roll against the target. If the attack misses, you cannot regain the function of this ability until after your next turn.</p>",
